movieDescription: Movie is about Aditya joins a law college in Vizag as a student. The law college is notorious for its unruly students headed by Satya (Rajeev Kanakala). Aditya is shown as a young mysterious man and throughout the first half there are several flashbacks to his story. He makes the unruly students mend their ways.

Movie start In 2044 the United States has suffered economic collapse causing severe social decay and growth in organized crime. In addition a strange mutation has occurred in 10% of the population, giving them minor telekinetic powers manifested by their ability to float small objects. They are referred to as TKs. Thirty years into the future in 2074, time travel is invented, but is immediately outlawed.
staring: Joseph Gordon-Levitt, Bruce Willis, Emily Blunt

movieDescription: Movie about yearning to start afresh and to disappear with his 10 yrs daughter Maddy the former DEA agent Phil Broker, relocates to Louisiana’s warm backwoods. However, Phil will soon find himself neck deep into trouble when a violent incident at Maddy’s school paves the way for a head-on confrontation with the local crystal meth dealer Gator and his cut-throat henchmen.
staring: Jason Statham, James Franco, Winona Ryder

movieDescription: Movie start with Casey Bowman the Westerner who was raised in a Dojo that trains Ninjas in Japan, is now in charge of the Dojo and married to Namiko the daughter of his teacher Takeda and is expecting a child. One day Namiko is killed in a gruesome manner and Casey is heartbroken.
staring: Scott Adkins, Kane Kosugi, Mika Hijii

movieDescription: Movie is about private UK based bodyguard Michael Bryce is hired to protect Takashi Kurosawa a Japanese arms dealer. All apparently goes well, until Kurosawa is shot in the head through an airplane window. Two years later, Bryce, fallen into disgrace, ekes out a living protecting drug-addicted corporate executives in London.
staring: Ryan Reynolds, Samuel L. Jackson, Gary Oldman

movieDescription: Movie is abut a special-force agent police officer is assigned to protect a young woman involved in a science experiment of longevity, from a gangster with an army of advanced technology who desires to obtain her power, while also having connections with him.
staring: Jackie Chan, Callan Mulvey, Tess Haubric

movieName: Master Z: The Ip Man Legacy
movieDescription: Movie story about while keeping a low profile after his defeat by Ip Man Cheung Tin Chi gets into trouble after getting in a fight with a powerful foreigner.
staring: Jin Zhang, Dave Bautista, Michelle Yeoh

movieDescription: Movie start with a guy who gets a face transplant done following a fire accident realises many are after his life. He sets out to find the reason for the same. Hos face is swapped with that of Sakthi’s. Siva who gets a new lease of life plans to start a business to take care of his family.

Film start with Satyaraj is old man who is diagnosed with lung cancer and is in his last stage of life. He informs this to his family and his grandson Sai takes lead and comes down to India and promises Satyaraj that he will make him spend the last few days with his family in peace. But Satyaraj’s sons have no time for their dad and reluctantly come to India.
staring: Sai Dharam Tej, Raashi Khanna, Sathyaraj

movieDescription: Movie story about a series of coincidences brings two star crossed lovers together but fate pulls them apart until they encounter each other again in Hyderabad. Mahi and Varsha are childhood friends who meet after 25 years. Very soon they get close and start liking each other. The couple decides to propose to each other but because of a health scare featuring Mahi, things fall apart all of a sudden.
staring: Shalini Pandey, Raj Tarun, Master Bharath

movieDescription: Movie is all about Corrupt Cop who is intelligent and brighter than normal people. A hidden treasure that is lost. A tribe called Adheeras is after the treasure but they cannot find it. Fifteen years pass by and a fancy cop Srimanarayana(Rakshit Shetty) comes into the picture and tries to trace the treasure.
staring: Rakshit Shetty, Shanvi Srivastava, Achyuth Kumar

movieDescription: Movie story start with Siddhu is a mamma’s boy who acts according to her will and joins a Btech course. In his college life he falls in love with Aishwarya. Right when the course is all set to be completed, Aishwarya breaks up with Siddhu and leaves him in distress. As time passes by, Siddhu meets Shruthi and falls in love with her. Right when the couple gets ready to propose each other, a sudden twist in the love story arises.
staring: Shiva Kandukuri, Varsha Bollamma, Malavika Satheesan

movieDescription: Movie is about keeps the viewer engaged is the fact that there are two separate tracks that run parallelly. A ghost named Maya becomes the common link between Arjun, an artist in London, and Sharmila, a single mom and struggling actress from Bengaluru. One is often left wondering what the connection between the two is. The film has all the tropes of a horror film – darkness, headless people and the works.

Movie story about Gana returns to India for his sister’s engagement after working in the US. Right when the function is going to happen, his sister attempts to kill herself. Gana saves her and shockingly finds out that his sister is pregnant and the father to her child is unknown. A helpless Shourya starts investigating this case and finally nabs the culprit.

Movie is about a widowed merchant is forced to move to the countryside after going bankrupt, with his six children, three sons and three daughters. His youngest daughter, Belle (Léa Seydoux) is the only one happy with the change. When one of the merchant’s ships is found, the merchant prepares to return to reclaim his assets.
staring: Vincent Cassel, Léa Seydoux, André Dussollier

movieDescription: Movie about stranded on a lonely road a schoolbus full of high school basketball players their coaches, and cheerleaders must defend themselves from the Creeper – a flesh-eating ancient beast that resurfaces on the earth every 23 years to feed. Meanwhile, a farmer and his son set out on a personal mission to hunt the Creeper down.
staring: Jonathan Breck, Ray Wise, Nicki Aycox
